reviewText: DVD was outdated, did not meet my need for students, only talked about floor nursing and did not explore other nursing positions.

It is not worth dime it is to costly and they don't take you on a tour show day to day care all they do is talk and info is repeat from online. You don't need this DVD, Trust me.-You will want send it back and loose have of the money paying for shipping.
A bit hokey and old fashioned, but a hoot for those who went through nursing education in times past. Great new condition and arrived timely.
